The challenges faced during this task.¶

  1. First challenge was to download the images URLs from image sources such as Google. To download multiple image URLs, language such as Javascript is used at web console.
  2. After the images are downloaded, the errorenous files/ images that were not correctly downloaded,need to be filtered out.
  3. All the image files need to be of same format and correct extension such as .jpg/.png/.jpeg etc.
  4. During downloading, some image sources might be restrictive.
